I made some modifications to a simple projectile motion trajectory graph in Desmos to make it more Rapid Reacty. Features include:

  • Adjustable launch height, angle, and speed,
  • Adjustable shooter offset,
  • Various target distances including from the fender, edge of the tarmac, and closer launchpad.
